Overall, a great purchase for the price.

To get increased battery life disable Hardware Accelerated GPU Scheduling.
It can be done as follows -
Settings --> System --> Display --> Graphics --> Default Graphics Settings -->
TURN OFF Hardware Accelerated GPU Scheduling.

Only turn on Hardware Accelerated GPU Scheduling while gaming because it significantly lowers the CPU temperature which in my case dropped from ~80¬∞C to ~65¬∞C.
